data.description:
Open House Sunday the 4th from 12:00 to 2:00.  Welcome to your dream home in The Crossings at Bartram community! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, 2-story residence is strategically located near various stores and restaurants, offering the perfect blend of convenience and comfort.

Situated within a quiet cul-de-sac, this home provides a serene and private retreat. The spacious layout begins downstairs with a large kitchen featuring an island, ideal for culinary enthusiasts. The open family and dining room areas create a welcoming space for entertaining family and friends.

For the convenience of your guests, there's a half bathroom located downstairs. Upstairs, you'll discover four generously sized bedrooms, offering versatility for various needs - whether it's a home office, guest room, or playroom.

The owner's suite is a true sanctuary, boasting a large walk-in shower, double sinks, and a spacious walk-in closet, ensuring ample storage space. Cont. The thoughtful design includes an upstairs laundry room for added convenience.

Step through the large sliding glass door, and you'll find yourself in the expansive backyard - a perfect canvas for outdoor activities, gatherings, or simply relaxing in your own private oasis. Additionally, residents of The Crossings at Bartram community have the luxury of enjoying a community pool without the cost of a CDD, creating the perfect setting for leisure and recreation.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort of living in this fantastic community!
